title: Supersize Me (Death by McDonald's) by Morgan Spurlock
description:
This film shows in a shocking way what will happen to you if you eat a Mc Donald's only true American diet. You will end up like millions of Americans, obese beyond description and finally be felled by cancer, hypertension, heart attack or other fatal diseases. But as usual corporate America denies all wrong-doing and, instead of improving America's diet, pours further millions into the system to keep Americans fat and ignorant. After all, the corrupt health system needs your money! 

Also watch Michael Moore's 'Sicko'.
